headline: ADM Board of Directors elects new member AT&T General Counsel David McAtee
summary: CHICAGO, November 06, 2024--ADM’s (NYSE: ADM) Board of Directors today announced that it has elected AT&T Inc. Senior Executive Vice President and General Counsel David R. McAtee II as its newest member. McAtee has served as AT&T’s worldwide General Counsel since 2015.
